- Added explicit equation tags so in-text references resolve to visible numbered display equations: `(1), (2), (4), (5), (8), (9), (10), (11), (15), (16), (20), (22), (23), (25), (27), (28), (29), (33), (35), (36), (46), (47), (48), (57)`.
